title: Well appointed home 3 bedroom house for rent in Port Orchard
posting_body: ['About This Home', 'Perfectly located at end of the street is this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Manchester!', 'On entry the light fill your eyes form the skylight, vaulted ceilings and large windows!', 'The foyer leads you through the formal living and dining room areas into the kitchen that has an open concept into the family room area.', 'Off the family room is a deck that looks out to the green belt, and private backyard.', 'Great areas for relaxing, and potential garden opportunities.', 'Upstairs are two generous sized guest rooms, a full bath and the primary bedroom, with walk in closet and en-suite.', 'Home is located 10 minutes to Southworth Ferry, and downtown Port Orchard.', 'Just a couple minutes from cute downtown Manchester and the dock and boat launch!', 'Move-in timeframe 45 days', 'Dogs and Cats are welcome!', 'House for rent', 'Basic Qualifications:', '-620 credit score', '-$85,000 household income', "-If the applicants can't meet the requirments listed above, a co-signer with a minimum credit score of 620 and a minimum annual income of 85,000 dollars can help get approval", '-No evictions', 'No felonies', '-Min 1 year Lease', 'Text Jing Now for Availability & Application', 'show contact info', '(Respond within 1 hours during working hours)']
